      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Descript has a neat feature where you can create an ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "artificial voice",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " by reciting a simple script.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.descript.com/ai-voices"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "You provide a sample of a voice, and Descript uses AI to generate a realistic synthetic version. This allows you to edit audio by simply typing text, and the AI will read it in your voice.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s not perfect. ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Yet",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ". It doesn't always capture every nuance perfectly, and sometimes the generated voice can miss certain inflections or sound a bit robotic.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The audio generated by Google’s new NotebookLM “audio overview” feature--which features two AI generated voices, one male and one female, who explain concepts in a podcast-esque dialog–is, however, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "astonishingly",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " realistic.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Here’s a ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "five-minute clip",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " of the pair reciting Descript’s voice training statement, and then explaining why the vocal exercise is crucial for mastering natural speech.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/30c725cc-c480-4e5b-ad9f-7dbe0851d383/audio"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s scary good. And it raises a lot of questions about what happens when a synthetic voice sounds exactly like a human.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Today is the worst that AI will ever be. We need to be cognizant of the challenges it brings as we embrace the potential that tomorrow’s AI holds.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}